trans-unit.source: Implements a type converter for <xref href="System.Windows.TemplateKey"></xref> objects, which deliberately have no type conversion pathways.
trans-unit.target: Implementa um conversor de tipos para <xref href="System.Windows.TemplateKey"> </xref> objetos, que é deliberadamente não tem nenhum caminhos de conversão de tipo.

trans-unit.source: The type converter enforces and reports that behavior.
trans-unit.target: O conversor de tipos impõe e reporta esse comportamento.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Windows.TemplateKey> type should not use a type converter pathway to convert values (should use markup extensions instead).
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Windows.TemplateKey>tipo não deve utilizar um caminho de conversor de tipo ao converter valores (deve utilizar as extensões de markup em vez disso,).</xref:System.Windows.TemplateKey>

trans-unit.source: For this reason, the <xref:System.Windows.Markup.TemplateKeyConverter.CanConvertFrom%28System.ComponentModel.ITypeDescriptorContext%2CSystem.Type%29> and <xref:System.Windows.Markup.TemplateKeyConverter.CanConvertTo%28System.ComponentModel.ITypeDescriptorContext%2CSystem.Type%29> methods always return `false`.
trans-unit.target: Por este motivo, o <xref:System.Windows.Markup.TemplateKeyConverter.CanConvertFrom%28System.ComponentModel.ITypeDescriptorContext%2CSystem.Type%29>e <xref:System.Windows.Markup.TemplateKeyConverter.CanConvertTo%28System.ComponentModel.ITypeDescriptorContext%2CSystem.Type%29>métodos sempre devolvem `false`.</xref:System.Windows.Markup.TemplateKeyConverter.CanConvertTo%28System.ComponentModel.ITypeDescriptorContext%2CSystem.Type%29> </xref:System.Windows.Markup.TemplateKeyConverter.CanConvertFrom%28System.ComponentModel.ITypeDescriptorContext%2CSystem.Type%29>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Windows.Markup.TemplateKeyConverter.ConvertFrom%28System.ComponentModel.ITypeDescriptorContext%2CSystem.Globalization.CultureInfo%2CSystem.Object%29> and <xref:System.Windows.Markup.TemplateKeyConverter.ConvertTo%28System.ComponentModel.ITypeDescriptorContext%2CSystem.Globalization.CultureInfo%2CSystem.Object%2CSystem.Type%29> methods always throw an exception.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Windows.Markup.TemplateKeyConverter.ConvertFrom%28System.ComponentModel.ITypeDescriptorContext%2CSystem.Globalization.CultureInfo%2CSystem.Object%29>e <xref:System.Windows.Markup.TemplateKeyConverter.ConvertTo%28System.ComponentModel.ITypeDescriptorContext%2CSystem.Globalization.CultureInfo%2CSystem.Object%2CSystem.Type%29>métodos sempre acionar uma excepção.</xref:System.Windows.Markup.TemplateKeyConverter.ConvertTo%28System.ComponentModel.ITypeDescriptorContext%2CSystem.Globalization.CultureInfo%2CSystem.Object%2CSystem.Type%29> </xref:System.Windows.Markup.TemplateKeyConverter.ConvertFrom%28System.ComponentModel.ITypeDescriptorContext%2CSystem.Globalization.CultureInfo%2CSystem.Object%29>
